thread.title: Michael Dambroseo
thread.title_full: Parts Town reviewed by Michael Dambroseo

author: Michael Dambroseo
title: Michael Dambroseo
text:
This company is a great supplier they get orders turned over quickly. Recently I placed a 2-day order with a competitor that got turned over to another vendor which required another two days and in this case the part was for myself ,but a customer would have been veryou upset if I promised them 2 days. So I would recommend Parts Town to anyone from my experience. Thank you very much for all the hard work you do at Partstown!
MFD
